{"tid":2048812,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"部分還柙手足約定於6月3日晚，在囚室默禱和唱《自由花》，而據知有網民將同日在荔枝角拘留所外舉行燭光晚會。","createTime":"2020-06-03T05:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T10:01:56.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2363ba09cd375da1de53b2122f74dcf8b34b9a96","tid":2048812,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T05:06:51.000Z","msg":"［轉載］<br />\n<br />\n我地係咪好耐無同還押緊既手足打氣<br />\n希望今晚見到大家<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200530&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60989997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200530%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60989997&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2Fxxga7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=2767d5d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200530%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60989997&h=fdf14a6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200530&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60989997</a><br />\n<br />\n【六四31】牆內悼念牆外聲援！在囚青年獄中悼六四被拒 無阻自由開花<br />\n<br />\n2020.05.30 00:05<br />\n<br />\n在「港版國安法」和限聚令下，每年六四在維園亮起的一片燭海或成絕響，但堅持了30年的香港人，並無忘記這段血的歷史，支聯會表示或採遍地開花形式紀念，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>而在反修例運動中被捕、並已還柙逾半年的抗爭者阿偉，更透過議員主動聯絡記者，透露悼六四祈禱會的申請雖被拒，但已與部份還柙手足約定於6月3日晚，在囚室默禱和唱《自由花》。而據知有網民將同日在荔枝角拘留所外舉行燭光晚會，實行牆內悼念牆外聲援，讓無法自由在維園亮起的燭光，以另一種自由的方式遍地開花。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qebVS4W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqebVS4W.jpg&h=1b7d3c1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n部分還柙手足約定於6月3日晚，在囚室默禱和唱《自由花》，而據知有網民將同日在荔枝角拘留所外舉行燭光晚會。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2048659\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2048659</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"674d166914269430685704bb145e20b70f72bff5","tid":2048812,"uid":308567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T05:13:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d22dad5845877fa925018e31837dfe059b7050b2","tid":2048812,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T05:22:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"943cdbd8bdf37c52cbad482dd6902abee2c5a7ec","tid":2048812,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T10:01:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}